Description: Photocure ASA is a Norway-based company active in the pharmaceutical industry. The Company is focused on developing and improving photodynamic technology and owns a Photocure Technology platform, which develops photodynamic technology for diagnosis and therapy. Based on the Photocure Technology platform, Photocure has developed and commercialized Hexvix (Hyperthermic IntraVEsical Chemotherapy) and Cysview (hexaminolevulinate HCL) for use in bladder cancer. The Companyâ€™s activities are divided into two business segments: The Commercial Franchise and The Development Portfolio. The Commercial Franchise segment includes Hexvix/Cysview by geography (U.S. and Europe) and other sales (partners and other products including sales revenues for Hivec). The Development Portfolio segment includes development of pipeline products.
